stories.text:
Hi all,

I'm looking for a co-working space in London and would like some recommendations. I used to work in Shoreditch in 2010s but on a recent visit it seems the startup vibe is not what it once was (granted, there's still pandemic going on).

Where are the entrepreneurs, startups and freelancers based today?

Backstory: I'm taking a month off work to build the company that I've always wanted to, maybe longer if it works out. I've always been passionate about interactive, immersive and 3D experiences and so this I will be looking for clients in this space. I've 10 years' experience as a software engineer and designer, having worked in video games and XR at big companies.

Thanks in advance! M
